{"lastUpdated":"2026-06-16T19:53:22.776Z","seriesId":518559,"title":"さすらいの太陽","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026132/45026132.12862965","descriptionFirst":"貧困のため辛い青春を送った看護婦の野原道子は、金持ちへの憎悪から裕福な香田家と貧しい峰家に同日に生まれた赤ん坊をすり替える。17年後、香田美紀は傲慢なお嬢様に、峰のぞみは快活な娘に成長した。道子は再びのぞみと美紀が高校の同級になるよう画策。2人の出会いで運命の幕が開く。\n\n声優:藤山ジュンコ、嘉手納清美、平井道子、井上真樹夫\n\n原作:藤川桂介・すずき真弓／監督:勝井千賀雄／演出:斧谷喜幸　\n\n©藤川桂介・すずき真弓・虫プロダクション\n\n次話→so45026138","tags":["アニメ","第一話"],"cours":null,"colKey":"さ","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so45026139","episodeNo":1,"title":"さすらいの太陽　第1話　「すりかえられた運命」","viewCounter":290,"startTime":"2025-05-31T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026139/45026139.15032089"},{"contentId":"so45026138","episodeNo":2,"title":"さすらいの太陽　第2話　「二つの誕生パーティー」","viewCounter":34,"startTime":"2025-05-31T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026138/45026138.64533410"},{"contentId":"so45026137","episodeNo":3,"title":"さすらいの太陽　第3話　「盗まれたメロデー」","viewCounter":42,"startTime":"2025-05-31T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026137/45026137.43651229"},{"contentId":"so45026136","episodeNo":4,"title":"さすらいの太陽　第4話　「私には歌がある」","viewCounter":40,"startTime":"2025-05-31T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026136/45026136.19201274"},{"contentId":"so45026135","episodeNo":5,"title":"さすらいの太陽　第5話　「初めてのアンコール」","viewCounter":22,"startTime":"2025-05-31T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026135/45026135.82647613"},{"contentId":"so45026134","episodeNo":6,"title":"さすらいの太陽　第6話　「訪れたチャンス」","viewCounter":19,"startTime":"2025-05-31T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026134/45026134.92163236"},{"contentId":"so45026133","episodeNo":7,"title":"さすらいの太陽　第7話　「歌を忘れたカナリア」","viewCounter":19,"startTime":"2025-05-31T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45026133/